node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 03, 2021 tagging @gritcapital. May be a Twitter screenshot of 1 person and text that says 'Genevieve Roch-Dector, CFA @GRDecter managed millions of dollars in investor money for nearly a decade and one of the funds ran with ~$30MM in assets average a 13% return for 7 years And let me tell you, there are some important lessons that learned.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 03, 2021 tagging @gritcapital. May be a Twitter screenshot of 1 person and text that says 'Genevieve Roch-Dector, CFA @GRDecter managed millions of dollars in investor money for nearly a decade and one of the funds ran with ~$30MM in assets average a 13% return for 7 years And let me tell you, there are some important lessons that learned.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 03, 2021 tagging @gritcapital. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'DECTER Genevieve Roch-Decter, CFA @GRDecter 1. Risk is fine in moderation. It's alright to make some risky investments here and there, but it shouldn't be a high % of your portfolio. 20% of my portfolio is dedicated to higher-risk investments.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 03, 2021 tagging @gritcapital. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Genevieve Roch-Decter, CFA @GRDecter 2. The best deals are private. Even though there are tons of great options to invest in with the open stock market, investing in private deals gives you access to more 10x and 100x opportunities.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 03, 2021 tagging @gritcapital. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Genevieve Roch-Dector, CFA @GRDecter 3.Big Big gains are nice, but consistent gains are key. Even though winning it big on some call options will give me you a nice screenshot, what really matters is your compound annual growth rate over 10, 20, or 30 years. don't like options.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 03, 2021 tagging @gritcapital. May be an image of text that says 'DECTER Genevieve Roch-Dector, CFA @GRDecter 4. Day trading is bad. This should be self-explanatory, but if Warren Buffet, the greatest investor of all time isn't making any trades, neither am I.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 03, 2021 tagging @gritcapital. May be a Twitter screenshot of 1 person and text that says 'DECTER Genevieve Roch-Dector, Roch CFA @GRDecter 5. Most people are better with ETF's. When it comes down to picking individual stocks, most people (even hedge funds) will not outperform basic EFTs like vOO and SPY over 30 years. If you can't beat them, join them.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 03, 2021 tagging @gritcapital. May be a Twitter screenshot of 1 person and text that says 'Genevieve Roch-Decter, CFA @GRDecter Now that I'm no longer managing other people's money, I'm your local financial meme dealer. make content that is both educating and entertaining while writing some newsletters every week. The best part? The content and one of my newsletters are free if you follow me.'.

So let's get started...'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 03, 2021 tagging @itskaibax. May be an image of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax In school, I was never the popular kid, I didn't have many friends and didn't really fit in. In fact, was getting severely bullied oullieo from 7th grade up until finishing high school. A few times it got to the point where we had to get the police involved.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 03, 2021 tagging @itskaibax. May be an image of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax Although school wasn't really an easy time for me, looking back, those times made me more independent and sparked my interest in business and personal development.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 03, 2021 tagging @itskaibax. May be an image of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax In high school, came across a social media marketing agency course. I realized could start that business because it didn't require a huge starting capital and could do it while was still at school. So I started my own agency.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 03, 2021 tagging @itskaibax. May be an image of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax In my last year of high school, started making $1-3K per month with my agency. It was nothing special but it was decent money at the time and it solidified that could eventually pursue my business full time.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 03, 2021 tagging @itskaibax. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax So in the final year of high school, had two options, either go to university or learn a trade. I never really saw myself pursuing either of those things and decided to start working full time on my marketing agency once I left school.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 03, 2021 tagging @itskaibax. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax I mostly got criticized for that but| didn't care and believed that made the right decision. So in September 2019 graduated from high schoo and my agency was making $1-3K at the time.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 03, 2021 tagging @itskaibax. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax By the end of 2019, scaled my agency to $20K per month. In 2020 $80K. had my record month of And in 2021 I've scaled my agency past $100K per month.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 03, 2021 tagging @itskaibax. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax So that is the story of how I've built built my agency over the past 2 years. If you'd like to learn more about building a social media marketing agency, drop me a follow.'.
